<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <header class="bg-gray-800 shadow p-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Guide</a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-indigo-400 hover:underline"
          >← Back to Home</a
        >
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-grow px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-400 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p class="mb-4 text-gray-300">
        We respect your privacy. This policy outlines how we collect and use
        your data while using this app.
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 text-gray-300">
        <li>
          <strong>Google Login:</strong> We store your name, email, and avatar
          only to personalize your experience. We do not share this information
          with anyone.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Search History:</strong> Logged-in users’ searches may be used
          for improving the app experience or cache results. We do not share or
          sell your data.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cookies & Sessions:</strong> We use secure session cookies to
          keep you logged in. No sensitive data is stored in cookies.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Third-Party APIs:</strong> This app uses the YouTube Data API.
          You are subject to Google’s own privacy policies as well.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p class="mt-6 text-gray-400 italic">
        This app is currently in development and not intended for commercial
        use.
      </p>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 py-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
      &copy; 2025 Guide. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
